quran[4{c,v,t}:
2,142,"nadaan log zaroor kahin ge : aِnhin kya howa ke pehlay yeh jis qble ki taraf rukh kar ke namaz parhte thay, is se yakayak phir gay? ae nabi, un se kaho :"" mashriq aur maghrib sab Allah ke hain Allah jisay chahta hai, seedhi raah dikha deta hai"
2,143,"aur isi terhan to hum ne tumhe aik"" ummat wast"" banaya hai taakay tum duniya ke logon par gawah ho aur rasool tum par gawah ho pehlay jis taraf tum rukh karte thay, is ko to hum ne sirf yeh dekhnay ke liye qibla muqarrar kya tha ke kon rasool ki pairwi karta hai aur kon ulta phir jata hai yeh maamla tha to bara sakht, magar unn logon ke liye kuch bhi sakht nah saabit howa, jo Allah ki hadaayat se Faiz yab thay Allah tumahray is imaan ko hargiz zaya nah kere ga, yaqeen jano ke woh logon ke haq mein nihayat shafeeq o Raheem hai"
2,144,"yeh tumahray mun ka baar baar aasman ki taraf uthna hum dekh rahay hain lau, hum usi qble ki taraf tumhe phairay dete hain, jisay tum pasand karte ho masjid haraam ki taraf rukh phair do ab jahan kahin tum ho, usi ki taraf munh kar ke namaz parha karo yeh log jinheinkitaab di gayi thi, khoob jantay hain ke ( tehweel qibla ka ) yeh hukum un ke Rab hi ki taraf se hai aur Bar haq hai, mgra iske bawajood jo kuch yeh kar rahay hain, Allah is se ghaafil nahi hai"
2,145,"tum un ahal kitaab ke paas khuwa koi nishani le aao, mumkin nahi ke yeh tumahray qble ki pairwi karne lagen, aur nah tumahray liye yeh mumkin hai ke un ke qble ki pairwi karo, aur un mein se koi giroh bhi dosray ke qble ki pairwi ke liye tayyar nahi hai, o ray agar tum ne is ilm ke baad jo tumahray paas aa chuka hai, un ki khwahisaat ki pairwi ki, to yaqeenan tumhara shumaar zaalmon mein hoga"
